el-modal-title elementor-inline-editing\" data-elementor-setting-key=\"title\" data-elementor-inline-editing-toolbar=\"basic\">Marc-Henri Balma<\/h4>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"uael-modal-text uael-modal-content-data clearfix\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"uael-text-editor elementor-inline-editing\" data-elementor-setting-key=\"ct_content\" data-elementor-inline-editing-toolbar=\"advanced\"><h5>Chief Operating Officer<\/h5>\n<p>Marc-Henri Balma ha iniziato la sua carriera in Credit Suisse. Successivamente ha lavorato per JP Morgan, Banque Labouchere, UBP e Edmond de Rothschild occupando varie posizioni dirigenziali nei settori IT, Operazioni ed in altre funzioni di supporto.<\/p>\n<p>Prima di entrare in Banque Cramer nel 2019, \u00e8 stato consulente senior e partner di Belmont Consulting Services. \u00c8 Chief Operating Officer di Banque Cramer e membro del Comitato esecutivo.<\/p>\n<\/div>\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"uael-overlay\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"uael-modal-action-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"uael-modal-action elementor-clickable uael-trigger elementor-inline-editing\" data-modal=\"3841b96\" data-elementor-setting-key=\"modal_text\" data-elementor-inline-editing-toolbar=\"basic\">\n\t\t\t\tLeggi il profilo\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-6e612a7\" data-id=\"6e612a7\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5d90272 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"5d90272\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"578\" height=\"323\" src=\"https:\/\/www.banquecramer.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/AMA.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-10850\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.banquecramer.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/AMA.png 578w, https:\/\/www.banquecramer.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/AMA-300x168.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 578px) 100vw, 578px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b6c8716 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b6c8716\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Andr\u00e9 S. Mankowsky<\/h4>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c3a957f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c3a957f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Head Private Banking<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bebdc93 elementor-widget elementor-widget-uael-modal-popup\" data-id=\"bebdc93\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"uael-modal-popup.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<div id=\"bebdc93-overlay\" data-trigger-on=\"text\" data-close-on-esc=\"yes\" data-close-on-overlay=\"yes\" data-exit-intent=\"no\" data-after-sec=\"no\" data-after-sec-val=\"1\" data-cookies=\"no\" data-cookies-days=\"1\" data-cookies-type=\"default\" data-custom=\"\" data-custom-id=\"\" data-content=\"content\" data-autoplay=\"no\" data-device=\"false\" data-async=\"\" class=\"uael-modal-parent-wrapper uael-module-content uamodal-bebdc93 uael-aspect-ratio-16_9 -popup\">\n\t<div id=\"modal-bebdc93\" class=\"uael-modal uael-center-modal uael-modal-custom uael-modal-content uael-effect-1   uael-aspect-ratio-16_9\">\n\t\t<div class=\"uael-content\">\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<span class=\"uael-modal-close uael-close-icon elementor-clickable uael-close-custom-popup-top-right\" >\n\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-times\"><\/i>\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"uael-modal-title-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"uael-modal-title elementor-inline-editing\" data-elementor-setting-key=\"title\" data-elementor-inline-editing-toolbar=\"basic\">Andr\u00e9 S. Mankowsky<\/h3>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"uael-modal-text uael-modal-content-data clearfix\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"uael-text-editor elementor-inline-editing\" data-elementor-setting-key=\"ct_content\" data-elementor-inline-editing-toolbar=\"advanced\"><h5>Responsabile Private Banking<\/h5>\n<p>Andr\u00e9 Mankowsky ha conseguito una laurea presso l'Universit\u00e0 di Friburgo e ha superato gli esami di avvocato a Ginevra nel 1995.<\/p>\n<p>Gode di una solida esperienza in campo finanziario e di pi\u00f9 di 25 anni nel settore bancario, principalmente nella gestione patrimoniale con particolare attenzione per la Russia, i paesi dell'Europa orientale ed i mercati emergenti. Ha ricoperto diverse posizioni manageriali all'interno di Credit Suisse, Deutsche Bank e Soci\u00e9t\u00e9 G\u00e9n\u00e9rale, in Svizzera, a Londra e Mosca.<\/p>\n<p>Nel gennaio 2021, \u00e8 entrato in Banque Cramer come responsabile del Private Banking, membro del Comitato esecutivo, con il mandato di aumentare l'impronta della banca all'interno dei suoi mercati principali.<\/p>\n<\/div>\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"uael-overlay\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"uael-modal-action-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"uael-modal-action elementor-clickable uael-trigger elementor-inline-editing\" data-modal=\"bebdc93\" data-elementor-setting-key=\"modal_text\" data-elementor-inline-editing-toolbar=\"basic\">\n\t\t\t\tLeggi il profilo\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"