a-id=\"fbf371c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Philippe Gougenheim<\/h4>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b406046 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b406046\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Head of Investment Services<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8d0b098 elementor-widget elementor-widget-uael-modal-popup\" data-id=\"8d0b098\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"uael-modal-popup.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<div id=\"8d0b098-overlay\" data-trigger-on=\"text\" data-close-on-esc=\"yes\" data-close-on-overlay=\"yes\" data-exit-intent=\"no\" data-after-sec=\"no\" data-after-sec-val=\"1\" data-cookies=\"no\" data-cookies-days=\"1\" data-cookies-type=\"default\" data-custom=\"\" data-custom-id=\"\" data-content=\"content\" data-autoplay=\"no\" data-device=\"false\" data-async=\"\" class=\"uael-modal-parent-wrapper uael-module-content uamodal-8d0b098 uael-aspect-ratio-16_9 -popup\">\n\t<div id=\"modal-8d0b098\" class=\"uael-modal uael-center-modal uael-modal-custom uael-modal-content uael-effect-1   uael-aspect-ratio-16_9\">\n\t\t<div class=\"uael-content\">\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<span class=\"uael-modal-close uael-close-icon elementor-clickable uael-close-custom-popup-top-right\" >\n\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-times\"><\/i>\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"uael-modal-title-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"uael-modal-title elementor-inline-editing\" data-elementor-setting-key=\"title\" data-elementor-inline-editing-toolbar=\"basic\">Philippe Gougenheim<\/h3>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"uael-modal-text uael-modal-content-data clearfix\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"uael-text-editor elementor-inline-editing\" data-elementor-setting-key=\"ct_content\" data-elementor-inline-editing-toolbar=\"advanced\"><h5>Head of Investment Services<\/h5>\n<p>Con un MBA conseguito alla ESSEC Business School, Philippe Gougenheim \u00e8 un professionista dell'Asset Management e del Wealth Management. Da 35 anni, le istituzioni pi\u00f9 rinomate, come JP Morgan, Soci\u00e9t\u00e9 G\u00e9n\u00e9rale e Millenium Partners, si avvalgono delle sue competenze in materia di investment banking, private banking e gestione di fondi.\u00a0Nel luglio 2016, Lombard Odier gli ha affidato, in qualit\u00e0 di Deputy Chief Investment Officer e Head of Global Markets, la coresponsabilit\u00e0 di un gruppo di oltre 200 gestori di \u00a0portafogli di clienti privati, nonch\u00e9 delle attivit\u00e0 di bilancio e di trading della banca.<\/p>\n<p><span lang=\"IT-CH\">Nell'aprile 2023, \u00e8 entrato a far parte della Direzione Generale di Banque Cramer come responsabile del Comitato Investimenti e membro del Comitato Esecutivo, apportando le sue competenze e professionalit\u00e0.<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"uael-overlay\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"uael-modal-action-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"uael-modal-action elementor-clickable uael-trigger elementor-inline-editing\" data-modal=\"8d0b098\" data-elementor-setting-key=\"modal_text\" data-elementor-inline-editing-toolbar=\"basic\">\n\t\t\t\tLeggi il profilo\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-b7152d1\" data-id=\"b7152d1\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-sec